{"tid":1682280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"石禮謙：從不支持逃犯條例修定 林鄭應聽年輕人聲音 社會求公義並非求買樓","createTime":"2019-10-30T03:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T16:41:58.000Z","uid":48631,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5858c15f08473a912ca21423792bb501d81381e7","tid":1682280,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5VPp39oPPBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5VPp39oPPBQ&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3zsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=4a248a1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5VPp39oPPBQ</a><br />\n中間好大部份都係石禮謙講返d人話，其實係啱聽嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我想講重點係喺頭同尾個度<br />\n簡單d講作為一個建制派，就算佢識得分是非黑白，佢都要繼續去盲撐政府，去保住個社會和諧穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家唔好期望有乜撚野開明建制派代替林鄭做特首，中共一吹雞明君都要變做屠夫"},{"pid":"e4de8ab5c85b9cb229c6d9b2c7579cae96d218f7","tid":1682280,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"54e2508dce1845d40f2e7fe967391d19628f2ee6","tid":1682280,"uid":100712,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:12:32.000Z","msg":"選舉近了"},{"pid":"9309cf5547d4bb0d1bffa8d20e1d3d1ab4a1326d","tid":1682280,"uid":334448,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"從來都冇開明建制派<br />\n只有忠誠嘅建制派同更忠誠嘅建制派<br />\n唔該之後叫佢地非民主派"},{"pid":"7626f4ac5d87f257feee22ab20ea16a90c364df7","tid":1682280,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T03:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ZaPUT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ZaPUT8.jpg&h=bd50a8b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6377b2da0d5365c85567e5023b49c22b5c45a60e","tid":1682280,"uid":48631,"lik